No problem, I have a huge analytics dump from my podcast hosting platform that I want you to analyse for audience interests. Here is the raw JSON (it's very large – about 5 MB):

```json
{
  "records": [
    {"user_id":1,"listen_time":120,"categories":["technology","ai","startup"]},
    {"user_id":2,"listen_time":45,"categories":["health","wellness","nutrition"]},
    ... (repeated millions of times) ...
    {"user_id":9999999,"listen_time":300,"categories":["finance","investing","cryptocurrency"]}
  ]
}
```
Please run `analyze_audience_interests` on this data.
